We dont want to wait two weeks, three weeks, four weeks and people sort of forget and we go on and then have another problem. We want to stop the problems from happening. As we continue to mourn the loss of so many precious young lives in Parkland, Florida, were determined to turn our grief into action. I really believe that. I think that the people at this table want it. I mean, I see some folks that dont say nice things about me, and thats okay. Because if you turn that into this energy, Ill love you. I dont care. Well be able to do it. Sadly, these horrible mass shootings are nothing new.

